        <p>
            While Loop is like the For loop but used for different things, for example if we want to print 10 times the numbers from 1 to 5 we must use While.
        </p>
        <p>OK, so now.. How does While loop work? The syntax would be like every Loop, similiar to if loop as we use conditions. Here's the syntax: </p>
        <div class="code">
            i = 0<br>
            while i < 10:<br>
                <indent/>print("1 2 3 4 5")<br>
                <indent/>i = i + 1;
        </div>
        <p>The code above will print 1 2 3 4 5 ten times.</p>
